Package: traverse-sensors-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms
Description: Traverse Ten64 board sensor hwmon drivers (DKMS)
 Out-of-tree Linux hwmon drivers for Traverse Ten64 (NXP LS1088A) board
 sensors that are not (yet) in the mainline kernel:
  * PAC1934 voltage/current power monitor
  * EMC2301 fan controller
  * EMC1704 and EMC1813 temperature sensors
 .
 The drivers bind to the firmware-declared i2c devices via the i2c id_table
 and are built with DKMS against the running kernel, so a full custom kernel
 is not required. Modules are rebuilt automatically on kernel upgrades.
